Package: alzio.detect
Title: Early Diagnosis Assessment for Alzheimer's Disease
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person("Dany", "Mukesha", , "danymukesha@gmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0001-9514-751X"))
  )
Description: A unified analytical toolkit for early Alzheimer's disease
    diagnosis assessment. Provides functions for cognitive test scoring and
    normative comparisons, biomarker interpretation, diagnostic classification,
    risk stratification, and visualization. Designed to work with data from
    common Alzheimer's studies (ADNI, NACC, custom datasets) to produce
    clinically interpretable diagnosis assessments.
